<IMG height=131 hspace=8 src="/images/photos/Motevo_Mobile_Media.jpg" width=200 align=left vspace=5>Motevo Mobile Media, Inc.&nbsp; cruises into the Day 4 spot of our <A href="/news/30daysInnovation.asp">30 Days of Innovation: A Countdown to CES</A> and&nbsp;onto the show floor bringing MOTor EVOlution to the 2009 CES. Motevo takes driving entertainment to a whole new level. Established just last year in California, Motevo Mobile Media, Inc. creates systems ripe with information and entertainment. They are a leader in infotainment systems and their systems are universal- made available no matter what make or model vehicle you drive. This in-dashboard technology can be easily installed and comes standard with a USB Port and DVD/CD support as well as optional Bluetooth Cell Phone Hands Free Interface. A touch screen and remote control make for easy access to unlimited media to keep drivers and passengers informed and entertained throughout road trips. Avoid getting lost or listening to the dreaded, “are we there yet?” by taking full advantage of Motevo’s innovative automotive systems.<BR><BR>Check out Motevo Mobile Media, Inc. in the LVCC, North Hall, Booth #1026. 
